Hussman Investment Trust - Hussman Strategic Growth Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 9:21 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Hussman Investment Trust - Hussman Strategic Growth Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Hussman Investment Trust - Hussman Strategic Growth Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Hussman Strategic Advisors, Inc. The fund invests in public equity markets of the United States. It invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in stocks of small-cap, medium-cap, and large-cap companies having market capitalizations in excess of $500 million. It employs  fundamental analysis with bottom-up stock picking approach by focusing on factors like relationship between its current market price and the present value of expected future cash flows per share, ratio of the stock price to earnings and stock price to revenue, valuati...
Hussman Investment Trust - Hussman Strategic Growth Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Hussman Strategic Advisors, Inc. The fund invests in public equity markets of the United States. It invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in stocks of small-cap, medium-cap, and large-cap companies having market capitalizations in excess of $500 million. It employs  fundamental analysis with bottom-up stock picking approach by focusing on factors like relationship between its current market price and the present value of expected future cash flows per share, ratio of the stock price to earnings and stock price to revenue, valuation, dividends, assets and liabilities, and market action to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Index. Hussman Investment Trust - Hussman Strategic Growth Fund was formed on July 24, 2000 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


5136 Dorsey Hall DriveFirst FloorEllicott City, MD 21042United StatesFounded in 2000



Phone: 410-715-1130

